title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Kharadron Overlords Codewright
description:
Armed with an aethershot pistol and a trusty battletome, Codewrights possess peerless knowledge of the Kharadron Overlords' grand constitution. Follow our step-by-step guide to get your Codewright ready for his next expedition using just 10 paints.  

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: warhammer.me/3Vkojs6

Don't forget to like, share and subscribe and to ring the bell to make sure you keep up to date with all our latest videos!
